snippet.textDisplay: Jaffer Zaidi is an absolute gem. an artist in the truest sense. As the soulful voice and creative force behind Kaavish, and the son of the legendary Nayyara Noor, music runs through his veins. The sound he produces transcends traditional genres—it's subtle, textured, and emotionally immersive. It's the kind of music that feels like poetry in motion, perfect for those quiet, reflective hours. Imagine a rainy night, moonlight filtering through the window, and the stillness of the dark around you—his music becomes a companion to your thoughts, wrapping you in its warmth and serenity. His compositions don't just entertain; they evoke, they linger, and they heal.

snippet.textDisplay: Heard from him for the first time... Was he telling me a story? Or was he consoling me? Or was he saying me sorry? Or was he expressing his love in his own way? Don't know answer to any of these... Kept asking myself, does he accept I "am" the main character of the story he was telling... Or was it just another lie of my dreams...!!! Who knows... No answer.... Just silence... The heart knows... But is the heart strong enough to accept the love it gets? Who knows... Just a story of our dreams...!!! Another lie...!!!
